we have to install vargent.
 $ vagrant up
 $ vagrant ssh mays
 $ cd /etc/ansible                 #we shoul head to the directory to download the dependencies
 $ ansible-galaxy install -r requirements.yml    # Zabbix Collection contains the roles for installing the Zabbix Server, Proxy, Agent, Javagateway and the Frond-end.

----# Installing Zabbix Server #----
 $ ansible-playbook -i hosts zabbix-server.yml
then we set groupsinside inventory file :
 cat > inventory.txt
 [zabbix_server]
target-1 ansible_host=172.20.48.81

[zabbix_database]
node-2 ansible_host=localhost

[zabbix_proxy]
node-3 ansible_host=10.10.1.13

[database:children]
zabbix_database
zabbix_proxy

$ansible-galaxy install dj-wasabi.zabbix-server
